      <h1 style="font-size:2.5rem;font-weight:800;line-height:1.2;margin-bottom:1rem;">
        Social Proof for Car Dealerships
      </h1>
      <p style="font-size:1.2rem;color:#555;margin-bottom:2rem;">
        Car buyers do 10+ hours of online research before they visit a dealership. By the time they walk through your door, they've already decided whether to trust you — based largely on what previous customers said. SocialProof helps dealerships collect genuine customer testimonials and display them where it matters: on your website, before the sale.
      </p>

      <h2 style="font-size:1.6rem;font-weight:700;margin-top:2.5rem;">Why testimonials matter more than inventory</h2>
      <p>Every buyer knows you have cars. What they don't know is whether buying from YOU will be a good experience. Dealership reviews affect decisions more than most industries — a car is one of the biggest purchases a family makes. Authentic testimonials on your website preempt the anxiety and skepticism buyers carry into the showroom.</p>

      <h2 style="font-size:1.6rem;font-weight:700;margin-top:2.5rem;">Testimonials that drive dealership sales</h2>
      <ul style="padding-left:1.5rem;line-height:1.9;">
        <li><strong>No-pressure experience:</strong> "I walked in dreading the usual sales tactics. Marcus listened, answered my questions, and never pushed. Best car buying experience I've had."</li>
        <li><strong>Fair pricing:</strong> "We agreed on a price quickly and it matched what I'd researched. No last-minute add-ons in the finance office."</li>
        <li><strong>Trade-in fairness:</strong> "They gave me $2,000 more for my trade than the other dealer. I drove home in my new car same day."</li>
        <li><strong>Service department:</strong> "Brought my car in for a recall. They had a loaner ready, finished same day, no charge. Phenomenal service."</li>
        <li><strong>Specific salesperson:</strong> "Ask for Jenna. She found me the exact trim I wanted in my color within 48 hours."</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 style="font-size:1.6rem;font-weight:700;margin-top:2.5rem;">How SocialProof works for auto dealers</h2>
      <ol style="padding-left:1.5rem;line-height:1.9;">
        <li><strong>Add the widget</strong> to your inventory pages, homepage, and service department page.</li>
        <li><strong>After delivery</strong>, send buyers your SocialProof link via text — when they're still excited about their new car.</li>
        <li><strong>Customers share naturally</strong> — no login, no app, just a simple text box.</li>
        <li><strong>Review and approve</strong> before any testimonial appears on your site.</li>
        <li><strong>Segment by department</strong> — sales testimonials on sales pages, service testimonials on the service page.</li>
      </ol>

